column5: For those thinking about fishing Couch this weekend,the CSFL Fall Challange is on.It is a two day tourney with about 50-70 boats.It,s a couch only tourney so it will be busy. Wiegh ins are at 3 pm blast off at 7 am.  This will be the last of the Cast For Cure  for me.I will post the final numbers Monday.  Now if I could just get my son whom is fishing with me, to stop calling and relax,I could get some poop done around here.LOL
And please dont think the guys are being rude when they dont wave back.It,s game time.
Good luck. I hope this cold front doesn't disrupt the fishing too much.  When your totals are in, I will be making a donation to you for Cast for a Cure.  Be safe my friend  John
Good luck Brian, I know you and your son will have a blast!  Looking forward to the report.  Maureen
You are probably in bed by now, but best of luck to you and junior this week-end! Be safe and make us all proud!
Good Luck Brian... can't wait for the report...
Good luck this weekend Brian, looking forward to the report.
